This was a project I started over two years ago, but never finished. I've started mapping again recently and decided to start by finishing this and releasing it.

All credit for the original surf goes to Archangel and Lethalis, their map was the one that I learned to surf on, and I wanted to do it justice by sticking as close to the original as possible.

I hope you enjoy surfing it as much as I enjoyed remaking this classic.

This is my 3rd surf map *yay*

===

FAQ:

Q: is there a buyzone in this map?
A: yes it's in the secret.

Q: how do i get to the secret?
A: it is behind the middle of spawns.

Q: how do i get out of the secret?
A: in the middle of the room is a button on the ceiling.

Q: why can't i shoot through the fence on jail?
A: cause i hate sniping campers everywhere. only campspot for them is in secret.

Q: why did i get a gun with only 1 clip.
A: you went to fast through the weapon spawner. it spawns bullets if u just walk through it.

My first surf map.
Inspired by surf_ambient made by razer and Pimp Juice
Halloween themed, tier 3, linear.
3 bonuses:
b1 by biji
b2 by Spy Complex
b3 by otter

sv_maxvelocity 10000

trigger_multiples for zones named according to zone type: mapstart, mapend, b1start, b1end, etc.

Bhop is allowed on anything within the main map(not any of the bonuses) that isn't triggered. You can bhop buildings, floors, spines, etc. Although, riding the spine of 2nd to last ramp is prohibited because it gives heavy headtilt. I added blockers but im sure someone will manage to avoid them anyway.

Straightforward surf map, my first of the kind. Any bugs, send an email to blackquaza [at] hotmail [dot] com

Completely re-done visuals (lighting, ect.)
